Exercise: Up and down pattern on each string

Pattern per string (up then down):
- Low E: A(5,f1) → C(8,f4) → C(8,f4) → A(5,f1)
- A string: D(5,f1) → E(7,f3) → E(7,f3) → D(5,f1)
