- B string: E(5,f1) → G(8,f4) → G(8,f4) → E(5,f1)
- High e: A(5,f1) → C(8,f4) → C(8,f4) → A(5,f1)

Notes in scale: A - C - D - E - G (pentatonic)

Finger positions:
f1 = Index (all 5th fret notes on E, A, B, e strings)
f2 = Middle (5th fret on D and G strings)
f3 = Ring (7th fret on A string)
f4 = Pinky (7th fret on D, G and 8th fret on E, B, e)

